<div class="container-sm">
    <h1 class="text-center"><%= title %></h1>
    <h3>About</h3>
    <p>Anistats is an open source project that generates statistics for AniList. It acts as an extension for the (really
        great!) already existing statistics page available on AniList profiles, and is not affiliated with AniList in
        any
        way.</p>
    <p>It is licensed under the <a href="https://github.com/LiterallyFabian/anistats/blob/master/LICENSE">MIT
            license</a>,
        and you can find the source code <a href="https://github.com/LiterallyFabian/anistats">here</a>.</p>

    <h3>Acknowledgements</h3>
    <p>This project is using the following tools and libraries:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/AniList/ApiV2-GraphQL-Docs">AniList API v2</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">Node.js</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/">NPM</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://expressjs.com/">Express</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/">WebStorm</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://ejs.co/">EJS</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://graphql.org/">GraphQL</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://datatables.net/">DataTables</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://getbootstrap.com/">Bootstrap</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://sass-lang.com/">SASS</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h3 id="privacy">Privacy</h3>
    <p>This project does not collect any personal data. It only uses the AniList API to generate statistics with public
        AniList profiles. The content of private AniList profiles is not accessible.</p>

    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions, comments, or suggestions, please contact me <a href="mailto:lindgrenfabian@gmail.com">here</a>.</p>
